构建环境因子图层

setwd("E:/otherWork/02_1/soil2019-rewrite/EnFactor")

files<-c("DEM.tif","Slope.tif","PlanC.tif","ProfileC.tif","TWI.tif","RSP.tif","LSF.tif","VD.tif","Bedrock.tif")

covStack <- raster(files[1])
for (i in 2:length(files)) {
  covStack <- stack(covStack, files[i])
}

#设置读取样点数据路径
point_shp_folder="E:/otherWork/02_1/soil2019-rewrite/shpPoint_allTrainingSamples/"

#设置最终结果tif的保存路径
result_tif_folder="E:/otherWork/02_1/soil2019-rewrite/result_mapTif/"

##设置随机数种子
set.seed(2019)

mn="All_pSNA_DEM_NS3_pen25" 

shpPoint<-readOGR(paste(point_shp_folder,mn,".shp",sep = "")) ###
## OGR data source with driver: ESRI Shapefile 
## Source: "E:\otherWork\02_1\soil2019-rewrite\shpPoint_allTrainingSamples\All_pSNA_DEM_NS3_pen25.shp", layer: "All_pSNA_DEM_NS3_pen25"
## with 594 features
## It has 1 fields
sampData <- extract(covStack, shpPoint, sp = TRUE,method = "simple") 

sampData<-sampData@data
sampData<-na.omit(sampData)
dim(sampData)
## [1] 591  10
sampData$soilID<-substring(as.vector(sampData$soilID),2,nchar(as.vector(sampData$soilID)))

sampData$Bedrock<-as.factor(sampData$Bedrock)  
sampData$soilID<-as.factor(sampData$soilID)

RF_model<-randomForest(soilID ~.,data = sampData, 
                       importance = TRUE, proximity = FALSE,ntree=1000,type="classification")

varImpPlot(RF_model)

print(RF_model)

                         "factor"=rep(NA,length(result_map_name)),
                         "NS"=rep(NA,length(result_map_name)),
                         "percent"=rep(NA,length(result_map_name)),
                         "precisionValue"=rep(NA,length(result_map_name)))

  fna<-result_map_name[i]
  ns_split<-unlist(strsplit(fna,"_"))
  if (length(ns_split)==5){
    precision_df[i,]$method<-ns_split[2]
    precision_df[i,]$factor<-ns_split[3]
    precision_df[i,]$NS<-ns_split[4]
    precision_df[i,]$percent<-ns_split[5]
    precision_df[i,]$precisionValue<-round( sum(vp_data$trueType==vp_data[fna])/nrow(vp_data),4)
  }
  else{
    precision_df[i,]$method<-ns_split[2]
    precision_df[i,]$factor<-ns_split[3]
    precision_df[i,]$NS<-"RAN"
    precision_df[i,]$percent<-ns_split[4]
    precision_df[i,]$precisionValue<-round( sum(vp_data$trueType==vp_data[fna])/nrow(vp_data),4)
  }
}

## [1] 92
multi_precision_df<-data.frame("method"=rep(NA,length(multi_result_map_name)),
                         "factor"=rep(NA,length(multi_result_map_name)),
                         "NS"=rep(NA,length(multi_result_map_name)),
                         "percent"=rep(NA,length(multi_result_map_name)),
                         "precisionValue"=rep(NA,length(multi_result_map_name)))

for (i in 1:length(multi_result_map_name)){
  fna<-multi_result_map_name[i]
  ns_split<-unlist(strsplit(fna,"_"))

  multi_precision_df[i,]$method<-ns_split[1]
  multi_precision_df[i,]$factor<-ns_split[3]
  multi_precision_df[i,]$NS<-ns_split[2]
  multi_precision_df[i,]$percent<-"pen75"
  multi_precision_df[i,]$precisionValue<-round( sum(multi_vp_data$trueType==multi_vp_data[fna])/nrow(multi_vp_data),4)

}

mfa<-unique(multi_precision_df$factor)
mfa_precision<-c()
for(mfai in mfa){
  i_split<-unlist(strsplit(mfai,"0"))
  temp_value<-round(mean(c(subset(precision_df,NS=="RAN" & percent=="pen75" & factor==i_split[1])$precisionValue,
                     subset(precision_df,NS=="RAN" & percent=="pen75" & factor==i_split[2])$precisionValue,
                     subset(precision_df,NS=="RAN" & percent=="pen75" & factor==i_split[3])$precisionValue)),4)
  mfa_precision<-c(mfa_precision,temp_value)
}


multi_precision_df_2<-data.frame("method"=rep("RAN",length(mfa)),
                         "factor"=mfa,
                         "NS"=rep("RAN",length(mfa)),
                         "percent"=rep("pen75",length(mfa)),
                         "precisionValue"=mfa_precision)

multi_precision_df<-rbind(multi_precision_df,multi_precision_df_2)
